UNSPONSORED REVIEW FT.MRUCHA BEAUTY 

Lush ink Markers 
-First these have the most thinnest consistency if you are getting any stain markers in the market  make sure you know that formulas like these any brand will settle on your lip lines if you layer alot. 
- personally I did not find them patchy for my lip liner and when filled apply a thin layer and spread to avoid more patches. 
- Are these for everyone I think not, cause it has a very specific use and if you want something like know what you are buying formula wise because they are ultimately like a sketch pen for your liner so the expectation should be the same, that being said I like the price point and the shades.
